cdata.name: XAYA
cdata.desc:
Rebranded from the Chimaera project, XAYA is a blockchain gaming platform. Its blockchain acts as a decentralized gaming backend that is scalable, secure and reliable. The XAYA platform is a continuously evolving environment facilitating developers with the tools they need to get their concept to market in less time with reduced cost.

The CHI is a utility token that works within the XAYA blockchain. It will serve the users as a medium for acquiring XAYA products such as apps and dapps (decentralized applications) as well as most of the features and services supported by the platform. In addition, transactions made between users on the platform can be performed using the CHI tokens.
